732
01:01:51,833 --> 01:01:53,292
- Kebakaran!
- Kebakaran!

733
01:01:54,127 --> 01:01:56,003
- Telepon pemadam kebakaran!
- Kebakaran!

734
01:01:56,087 --> 01:01:58,464
- Apa-apaan?
- Kebakaran!

735
01:01:58,548 --> 01:02:01,718
Kebakaran!

736
01:02:01,801 --> 01:02:03,052
Awas!

